<a id="more"></a>
<h3 id="Html"><a href="#Html" class="headerlink" title="Html"></a>Html</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;html lang=<span class="string">"ZH-CN"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;head&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;meta charset=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;meta name=<span class="string">"keywords"</span> content=<span class="string">""</span>/&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;meta name=<span class="string">"description"</span> content=<span class="string">""</span>/&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;link rel=<span class="string">"shortcut icon"</span> href=<span class="string">""</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;title&gt;20170113 goast&lt;/title&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;link <span class="built_in">type</span>=<span class="string">""</span> rel=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> href=<span class="string">"style/0113.css"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/head&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;body&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;div class=<span class="string">"box"</span>&gt; </div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=<span class="string">"link link-miss"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;span class=<span class="string">"icon"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;a href=<span class="string">"#"</span> class=<span class="string">"button"</span> data-title=<span class="string">"My mission clear"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-top"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-left"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-bottom"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-right"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				MISSION</div><div class="line">			&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=<span class="string">"link link-play"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;span class=<span class="string">"icon"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;a href=<span class="string">"#"</span> class=<span class="string">"button"</span> data-title=<span class="string">"This is my palyground"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-top"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-left"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-bottom"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-right"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				PLAY</div><div class="line">			&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=<span class="string">"link link-touch"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;span class=<span class="string">"icon"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;a href=<span class="string">"#"</span> class=<span class="string">"button"</span> data-title=<span class="string">"Let's do something together"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-top"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-left"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-bottom"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				&lt;span class=<span class="string">"line line-right"</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">				TOUCH</div><div class="line">			&lt;/a&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;div class=<span class="string">"tip"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt; &lt;!--提示性文字--&gt;</div><div class="line">			&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</div><div class="line">		&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;/div&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;script src=<span class="string">"http://libs.baidu.com/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">	&lt;script src=<span class="string">"js/0113.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">		</div><div class="line">&lt;/body&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;/html&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Css"><a href="#Css" class="headerlink" title="Css"></a>Css</h3><blockquote>
<p>这里涉及部分css3属性，所以对于低版本的browser的支持效果不是很好</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">body&#123;background: <span class="comment">#333;font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei';&#125;</span></div><div class="line">a&#123;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;&#125;</div><div class="line">.box&#123;width:800px;height:280px;margin: 50px auto;&#125;</div><div class="line">.box .link&#123;width:205px;height:280px;margin:10px 20px;<span class="built_in">float</span>:left;position:relative;&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">.link .icon&#123;width:100%;height:190px;display:block;transition:all 1s linear;-webkit-transition:all 1s linear;-moz-transition:all 1s linear;-ms-transition:all 1s linear;&#125;</div><div class="line">.link-miss .icon&#123;background: url(<span class="string">'../images/mission.png'</span>) no-repeat center center;&#125;</div><div class="line">.link-play .icon&#123;background: url(<span class="string">'../images/play.png'</span>) no-repeat center center;&#125;</div><div class="line">.link-touch .icon&#123;background: url(<span class="string">'../images/touch.png'</span>) no-repeat center center;&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">.link .icon:hover&#123;-webkit-transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1.1); -o-transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1.1);-moz-transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1.1);-ms-transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1.1);&#125;</div><div class="line">.button&#123;display:block;font-size:16px;font-weight:bolder;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.8);padding-left:20px;margin: 0 auto;width:180px;height:50px;line-height:50px;color: <span class="comment">#2dcb70;box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-box-sizing:border-box;-moz-box-sizing:border-box;background: url('../images/allow.png') /*设置背景指示图位移*/ no-repeat 130px 50%;position:relative;transition:all 0.3s ease;-webkit-transition:all 0.3s ease;-moz-transition:all 0.3s ease;-ms-transition:all 0.3s ease;&#125;</span></div><div class="line">.button:hover&#123; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,1);background-position:140px center;&#125;</div><div class="line">.button  .line&#123;display:block;position:absolute;background:none;transition:all 0.2s ease;-webkit-transition:all 0.2s ease;-moz-transition:all 0.2s ease;-ms-transition:all 0.2s ease;&#125;/*过渡效果必须放在初始值*/</div><div class="line">.button:hover .line&#123;background:<span class="comment">#fff;&#125; /*background:#fff背景色为白色*/</span></div><div class="line">/*1、高度不变 2宽度在变 3位置在变*/</div><div class="line">.button .line-top&#123;height:2px;width:0px;left:-110%;top:-2px;&#125;</div><div class="line">.button:hover .line-top&#123;width:100%;left:-2px;&#125;</div><div class="line">.button .line-bottom&#123;height:2px;width:0px;right:-110%;bottom:-2px;&#125;</div><div class="line">.button:hover .line-bottom&#123;width:100%;right:-2px;&#125;</div><div class="line">/*1、宽度不变 2高度在变 3位置在变*/</div><div class="line">.button .line-left&#123;width:2px;height:0;left:-2px;bottom:-110%;&#125;</div><div class="line">.button:hover .line-left&#123;height:100%;bottom:-2px;&#125;</div><div class="line">.button .line-right&#123;width:2px;height:0;right:-2px;top:-110%;&#125;</div><div class="line">.button:hover .line-right&#123;height:100%;top:-2px;&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">.box .tip&#123;position:absolute;padding:0 14px;height:35px;line-height:</div><div class="line">35px;background: <span class="comment">#2dcb70;color:#fff;top:160px;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;/*uppercase;capitalize;lowercase转换不同文本的大小写*/margin:0 auto;border-radius:3px;opacity:0;/*透明度为0隐藏*/&#125;</span></div><div class="line">.tip em&#123;font-style:normal;&#125;</div><div class="line">.tip span&#123;width:0;height:0;overflow:hidden;left:50%;margin-left:-3px;</div><div class="line">	position:absolute;top:100%;border:7px solid transparent;border-top-color: <span class="comment">#2dcb70;/*倒三角*/</span></div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="这里有必要提一下几个知识点："><a href="#这里有必要提一下几个知识点：" class="headerlink" title="这里有必要提一下几个知识点："></a>这里有必要提一下几个知识点：</h4><ul>
<li><p><code>background</code>属性<br><br>eg:body{background: #00FF00 url(bgimage.gif) no-repeat fixed top;}<br><br>可能的值：<br>background-position 规定背景图像的位置。<br>background-size    规定背景图片的尺寸。<br>background-repeat 规定如何重复背景图像。<br>background-origin 规定背景图片的定位区域。<br>background-clip    规定背景的绘制区域。<br>background-attachment 规定背景图像是否固定或者随着页面的其余部分滚动。    </p>
</li>
<li><p><code>transition</code>属性<br><br>eg:div<br>{<br>width:100px;<br>transition: width 2s;<br>-moz-transition: width 2s; /<em> Firefox 4 </em>/<br>-webkit-transition: width 2s; /<em> Safari 和 Chrome </em>/<br>-o-transition: width 2s; /<em> Opera </em>/<br>}<br>语法:<br>transition-property    规定设置过渡效果的 CSS 属性的名称。<br>transition-duration    规定完成过渡效果需要多少秒或毫秒。<br>transition-timing-function    规定速度效果的速度曲线。<br>transition-delay    定义过渡效果何时开始。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>注意：<code>transition</code>属性必须设置在代码的初始值里</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><code>text-transform</code>属性<br><br>text-transform:转换不同文本的大小写，值有：uppercase(大写);capitalize(首字母大写);lowercase(小写)</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="Javascript"><a href="#Javascript" class="headerlink" title="Javascript"></a>Javascript</h3><blockquote>
<p>这里用到jquery<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$(<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>()&#123;</div><div class="line">	$(<span class="string">'.link .button'</span>).hover(<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>()&#123;</div><div class="line">		var title = $(this).attr(<span class="string">'data-title'</span>);</div><div class="line">		$(<span class="string">'em'</span>).text(title); //em承载的内容就是title</div><div class="line">		var pos = $(this).offset().left;</div><div class="line">		var dis = ($(<span class="string">'.tip'</span>).outerWidth() - $(this).outerWidth())/2;</div><div class="line">		var f = pos - dis;</div><div class="line">		$(<span class="string">'.tip'</span>).css(&#123;<span class="string">'left'</span>:f+<span class="string">'px'</span>&#125;).animate(&#123;<span class="string">'top'</span>:<span class="string">'190'</span>,<span class="string">'opacity'</span>:<span class="string">'1'</span>&#125;,300);;</div><div class="line">	&#125;,<span class="function"><span class="title">function</span></span>()&#123;</div><div class="line">		$(<span class="string">'.tip'</span>).animate(&#123;<span class="string">'top'</span>:160,<span class="string">"opacity"</span>:<span class="string">'0'</span>&#125;,300);</div><div class="line">	&#125;);</div><div class="line">	</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="总结："><a href="#总结：" class="headerlink" title="总结："></a>总结：</h3><ul>
<li>1.位移的计算：<code>var pos = $(this).offset().left;<pre><code>var dis = ($(&apos;.tip&apos;).outerWidth() - $(this).outerWidth())/2;
var f = pos - dis;&lt;/code&gt;
</code></pre></code></li>
<li>2.很多css3属性</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
    
